&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Statistics:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;strong background in statistical reasoning and methods for evaluating change and uncertainty.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coding:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;strong Python and SQL; you can independently run experiments and ship analyses and pipelines end to end.&lt;/li&gt;
