&lt;li&gt;Direct experience with optimization, MPC, and system dynamics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with data analysis and statistical methods applied to real-world sensor/vehicle data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to guide the technical direction of a small team while remaining a strong individual contributor.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication and collaboration skills, with a focus on delivering results and driving cross-team alignment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
