&lt;li&gt;Digital signal processing techniques for analyzing real-world sensor data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced knowledge of mathematics, including optimization, probability, and mechanics, and a proven ability to translate complex theory into production-ready algorithms.&lt;/li&gt;
