&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Curate and Manage Large-Scale Datasets:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Oversee data collection, preprocessing, and augmentation to maintain high-quality datasets for training and evaluation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enhance and Maintain Training Pipelines:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Develop efficient workflows for training, validation, and testing, incorporating distributed training, hyperparameter tuning, and automated monitoring.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Improve Model Deployment and Efficiency:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Optimize inference performance, model compression, and deployment across various hardware platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Explore and Apply Cutting-Edge ML Techniques:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Stay up to date with advancements in deep learning and experiment with novel approaches to improve model performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate with Cross-Functional Teams:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Work closely with researchers, software engineers, and robotics experts to integrate machine learning solutions into real-world autonomous systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;heading-2&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll need&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of fundamental machine learning algorithms and neural network techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in at least one modern machine learning domain, such as computer vision, large language models, or generative AI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least three years of experience developing neural network-based algorithms, including data collection, training, and deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
